Metal Price Sensitivity:
        In preparing the sensitivity analysis, we recalculated our reserves based on the assumption that current average metal prices were
20% higher and 20% lower , respectively , than the actual current average prices for year -end 2018. Reserve results of this sensitivity
analysis are not proportional to the increase or decrease in metal price assumptions.
