        Pension and post retirement obligations include the benefits expected to be paid under our pension and post-retirement benefit
plans. Please refer to Note 1 1 "Benefit Plans" of our consolidated financial statements.
        Asset retirement obligations include the aggregate amount of the closure and remediation costs of our Peruvian mines and
