Long-term debt (in millions):
 
        The bonds, referred above as "Y ankee bonds", contain a covenant requiring Minera Mexico to maintain a ratio of EBITDA  to
interest expense of not less than 2.5 to 1.0 as such terms are defined in the debt instrument. At December 31, 2018, Minera Mexico
was in compliance with this covenant.
